ormed, including the gymnastics competition at the newly revived Olympic Games in Athens in 1896.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999867418411, \"rank\": 1.3258182800388157e-08, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"popularity\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"the 19th century\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"an increasing number\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnastics competition\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"the newly revived Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Artistic gymnastics is composed of a number of individual competitions on different apparatus, as well as a team competition involving gender-specific apparatus.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Artistic gymnastics\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"individual competitions\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"different apparatus\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"a team competition\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2172}, {\"ngram\": \"gender-specific apparatus\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each piece of apparatus requires different skills.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each piece\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"apparatus\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"different skills\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Men compete across the f